'''Eugen Systems''' is a [[France|French]] [[video game developer]] based in [[Paris]], [[France]]. It was founded in January 2000 by Alexis Le Dressay, a [[:fr:Architecte diplômé par le gouvernement|DPLG]] architect, and Cedric Le Dressay, a software engineer.<ref name="name">{{cite web|url=http://www.eugen.fr/|title=Eugen Systems|publisher=eugen.fr|accessdate=2016-05-14}}</ref> The company currently focuses on developing [[real-time strategy]] games for the [[Personal computer|PC]] and [[Macintosh]] platforms, but also has developed games for the [[PlayStation 3]] and [[Xbox 360]] in the past.<ref name="name">{{cite web|url=http://www.eugen.fr/|title=Eugen Systems|publisher=eugen.fr|accessdate=2016-05-14}}</ref>

